.s_11637015 { telerik-style-type: local;font-weight: bold;font-size: 18.6666666666667px;color: #3FB3EC;background-color: #FFFFFF; } </style></head><body><p class="Normal "><span class="s_28145731">Web-based Admin Panel</span></p><p class="Normal ">Fleet management system designed to boost employee&rsquo;s wellbeing, through a user-friendly interface admin will be able to create, manage, and report employee&rsquo;s check-ins and outs with remarks.</p><p class="Normal ">&nbsp;</p><p class="NormalWeb p_582AFDA0"><img width="150" height="53" src="data:image/png;base64," /><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.softexsw.gps.tracker" target="_blank"></a><span class="s_11637015">Mobile Application for employees&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></p><p class="Normal ">&nbsp;</p><p class="Normal ">Trustworthy and accuracy and to make employees experience world-class, this is the main factors to start using Softex GPS Tracking mobile application.</p><p class="Normal ">&nbsp;</p><p class="Normal ">To let users, feel comfortable that their efforts are not wasted, by locating and reporting to their leaders with a detailed summary from both sides, Softex GPS Tracker generate accurate location data whatever the end-user (Employee) is connected to the internet or not, and once connected again all the data shall be sent to the admin panel.</p></body></html>
